name: Felt Peg-bag
description: This cute felt peg-bag, has been hand stitched with love and care. The bag measures 30cm in length, plus 9cm for the hook at the top, by between 22 and 23cms in width. This can vary slightly as these are handmade. These can be made to order (which would take about a week) I currently have the following stock: Pale pink with silver hearts, with a pale pink backing Blue / green tie-dye, with a green backing Ladybird patterned, with a white backing Leopard print, with a black backing Red polka dot, with a white backing Purple with yellow flowers, with a yellow backing

name: Purple Fairy Wings
description:
Wings - Inspired by Emilie Autumn

These lovely fairy wings have black ribbons to fasten over your arms, and trailing ribbons of at least 50 cms. They are entirely handmade, painted, and embellished with diamente teardrops.

Wingspan 67cm wide x 49cm high.

Photographed in purple - why not request a different colour (currently taking up to 1 month made to order)

name: Button, Bead and Sequin Tree
description:
This is a christmas tree with a difference... or an any occasion tree for that matter! It is adorned with buttons, beads and sequins for your viewing pleasure.

This tree is pink / red, and stands 20 centimetres tall with a felt base so as not to scratch your surfaces.

name: Earrings (various)
description:
These earrings feature Czech Glass beads, with a combination of seed, bugle and rocaille beads to compliment.

All the findings are hypoallergenic surgical steel, silver in colour.

options.name: Single Czech Glass Earrings with bugle beads

name: Blue Butterfly Ribbon Necklace
description:
A beautiful glass butterfly with dark blue, turquoise, lilac and silver metallic colours running through, similar to dichroic glass.

It is threaded on silver organza ribbon along with an accent lilac ribbon.

Along the ribbon are glass accent beads of two shades of blue, 6 beads in total.

This necklace is 49cm long, and is finished with silver crimps, split rings and a trigger clasp.
